      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "It‚Äôs fine for experienced, high-net-worth individuals to bet their own money on alternative investments, just like wealthy collectors have long dabbled in the rare-book trade. But this is different: This is public officials gambling public pensioners‚Äô retirement savings on opaque and risky schemes.",
